| Phase | Difficulty        |
| ----- | ----------------- |
| A     | easy              |
| B     | medium            |
| C     | easy              |
| D     | medium            |
| E     | 🔥 interesting    |
| F     | 🔥🔥 hard         |
| G     | 🔥🔥🔥 real value |

---

# 🚀 My recommendation (very concrete)

Do this next:

---

## Step 1 (today)

👉 Phase A + B (just get graph from llm-tldr)

---

## Step 2 (tomorrow)

👉 Phase C + D (query API)

---

## Step 3 (then)

👉 Phase E (your expansion — THIS is the moment)

