# 🔥 What makes a *good* metamorphic relation

This is the important part.

A good relation is:

### ✅ invariant-based

```text
should always hold
```

### ✅ transformation-aware

```text
explicitly tied to how input changed
```

### ✅ not too strict

```text
doesn’t require exact equality unless appropriate
